{"tid":1642103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 馬蹄露聽日會現身中環!","createTime":"2019-10-09T14:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T15:16:46.000Z","uid":273051,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3031eebcd08a28a2f3f1d4ea117e88c644aee2","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">屌! 你地班中環友好唔好意思呀?</span> <br />\n<br />\n前線勇武, 中學生都可以為左我地和理非擋子彈! 要你地每日lunch time岀黎行, 嗌口號, 係咪好撚難為你地呀? 可以做運動強身健體, 又可以做文宣! <br />\n<br />\n仆你個街! 仲有人問我, 每日都岀好攰嫁喎... 我屌你啦! 我地係<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Water Revolution!</strong></span></span> 唔撚係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Weekend Revolution</span></strong></span>呀! 你地唔好公眾假期先岀? <br />\n<br />\n好! 我就當你地今日全部去哂做護琦手, 所以無岀. 聽日俾多機會你地, 同我岀黎! <br />\n<br />\n趁呢個機會話俾國際知, 我地爭取民主自由既決心! 民主係唔由個天跌落嚟嫁! 仲有大概六日就知美國民主人權法案過唔過...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢段時間最好就係我地和理非接力, 一個作為香港金融既中心, 中環友一定要岀黎行! </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RMEeAar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRMEeAar.jpg&h=342cdf33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c40b1c76d487c08a8b0c93bc0744f6af208c6fc4","tid":1642103,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線要人!！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢排國際上發生左幾單重要打<br />\nNBA、south park 、暴雪、red bull <br />\n大家點可以呢個時候懶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>係時候要世界明白中國有幾醜惡!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線！全球抗共！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n任務：<br />\n1. Twitter 戰線 請用Tg入面既Twitter help<br />\n2 YouTube 英文短片<br />\n3. Reddit戰線</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地只有令全世界明白香港係幫自由世紀抵擋邪惡國家既先鋒，先可以令世人支持我地！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770a962c05b2a96ddb8d080f3c007a3ce3d2e08c","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"自推 <br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"52d37571b6183d956900225a2f82aef2d449e2c2","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770a962c05b2a96ddb8d080f3c007a3ce3d2e08c","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"自推 <br />\n1/10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"acf0a6fa9313ed2428dce170c80e4fb76a9eb1c2","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d37571b6183d956900225a2f82aef2d449e2c2","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770a962c05b2a96ddb8d080f3c007a3ce3d2e08c","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"自推 <br />\n1/10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"2/10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"3bf97fe720605e88ba9923110cbea65e9f935603","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf0a6fa9313ed2428dce170c80e4fb76a9eb1c2","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d37571b6183d956900225a2f82aef2d449e2c2","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770a962c05b2a96ddb8d080f3c007a3ce3d2e08c","tid":1642103,"uid":273051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"自推 <br />\n1/10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim